          <h4>In-depth</h4>
          <p>Research-validated online assessment with 26-page management-specific report helps managers understand:</p>
          <ul>
              <li>Themselves </li>
              <li>Their employees </li>
              <li>Their bosses </li>
          </ul>
          <h4><strong>Easily customisable </strong></h4>
          <p>Remove or rearrange pages, customise the report title, or print selected sections. This profile may be used on its own or with the companion facilitation (sold separately).</p>
                
          <h4>View Samples:</h4>

